  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a result of this technique, the user can create convincing false tracks that can throw a tracker off course. The time is reduced by 1 minute (minimum 5 rounds) for every 3 points the user beats the skill threshold and perform DC by.<br><br>Anyone tracking the user encountering the false tracks must make a Survival DC 15 or make a new Survival check to track them at a -5. This penalty persists until the tracker successfully makes the check.<br><br>If the Survival check fails by 10 or more, they lose the trail and for the next 1 minute take a -10 to checks to track them. After which, they take the aforementioned -5 until they make the check.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> : Track (f)</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step of mastery increases the Survival DC by 1.</p>\n",
